subject: Thanks for the great resources!

messageBody:
Just started teaching myself Quickscript on Tuesday, and on Wednesday was thinking to myself "it would be really cool if I could practice reading a story like Call of Cthulhu or something."  And there it is!  I'm only into the second paragraph, as I'm trying to be thorough and I haven't had much time to practice, but I'm looking forward to practising more!
-Tev
